{"id": "1406934394874105947", "channel_id": "1406934394874105947", "type": 0, "author_id": "194872366780645376", "author_name": "snowvleopard", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm sorry if this is the wrong channel or inappropriate to suggest but I didn't know where else to post this 😭... \n\nMaybe I'm just blind but I noticed there are Instagram accounts for neither the game nor the developing studio so I just wanted to suggest for the game to also have some presence on Instagram maybe 💖 I'm not sure if it's too much work to manage/ too expensive or if it's actually a planned choice, but it might help gain more players if people can follow and tag the account with their fan creations like fanart, videos or cosplay or other content? I'm a cosplayer and artist myself and absolutely want to do a Morimens cosplay too in the future...so don't be shy and let me and the other content creators tag you guys <:rizz:1172627562095198228>\n\nAlso please upload more of the OSTs on spotify, they're so beautiful and it's sad that there's only the few tracks on there so far 🏃🏃🏃🏃  (And I hope that one day you will maybe exhibit at trade fairs like Gamescom!!)", "timestamp": "2025-08-18T09:34:59.315000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Emoji_LY_L_07", "emoji_id": "1400771686965444648", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1406934394874105947", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Instagram + more OSTs on Spotify", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
{"id": "1407085166781792386", "channel_id": "1407085166781792386", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "Kathigu-ra is a pretty nice unit and it can be very strong, but the difference from E0 and E3 is to much, her gameplay is severely impeded if she don't have those initial Fiamma stacks, limiting her viability and enjoyment. \nI hope that, like for Doresain, that mechanic can be integrated in her base kit, reworking the E3 bonus and, to compensate, potentially slightly lowering the scaling with Combustion stacks to account for it.\nThe point is to make her still strong if invested but not as bad at base level, considering that she is out at the same time as a very loaded rerun, so heavy investing is an harder ask.", "timestamp": "2025-08-18T19:34:06.139000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-18T19:36:03.169000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1407085168602124388", "filename": "sss-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 9904641, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1407085166781792386/1407085168602124388/sss-.jpg?ex=69ff8c2e&is=69fe3aae&hm=fbed271813b0e9edcf05ea912fdc1bbe6d2c074b3f8edd82d0092f2a5669d646&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1407085166781792386", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Potential changes for Kathi", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
